snippet.title: Arcade Game: The End (1980 Konami)
snippet.description:
A shooting game in the style of galaxian and space invaders. You must shoot all bugs before you run out of lives. Or the bugs will use  the eggs to spell the word "END". Then the game is over.

Other names for this game is Omega.
